This dessert is fabulous. It is so simple and yet is always a big hit with everyone. I made it with fresh whipped cream and used some left over vanilla custard sauce (from this site) that I had. Would also be good with blue berries.

Rating: 4
I brought this dish to a neighborhood Bingo and everyone loved it. I did not peel the peaches and I put them out on a platter with a bowl of fresh whipped cream that I added a bit of brown sugar to. It was wonderful! It's nice to have a great dish like that to share that doesn't require much time or effort!

